      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus: £100m Zoo Animals Fund application deadline extended
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The deadline for applications for the £100m Zoo Animals Fund has been extended until 29 January 2021</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
